                            <comment id="15145365" author="eyal" created="Fri, 12 Feb 2016 21:48:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch fixes the bug by removing the static modifier, and adds a new test to check for this case. I also changed the order of the main conditional in the exec method, because checking the boolean (which is fast) should come before the pattern matching (which is slower).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15146955" author="daijy" created="Mon, 15 Feb 2016 06:29:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Committed to both trunk and 0.15 branch since this leads to wrong result.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks Eyal!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
